-- Attorney Silvana Raso Discusses `Business Divorces' (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2012-05-23T14:20:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-23/attorney-silvana-raso-discusses-business-divorces-audio-.html
Silvana Raso, partner at Schepisi and
McLaughlin, discusses the process of legal separation of 
business partners when they decide to no longer remain in 
business together. Raso talked to Bloomberg's  Kathleen Hays  and 
Vonnie Quinn on "The Hays Advantage" on Bloomberg Radio on May 
22, 2012.  (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 08:13
 